      "date": "2012-11-25 19:15:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/23cbf91e-372e-11e2-8203-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  2 tests failed: mmp, replay-single.",
